// Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2024-2113 — Mass File Rename (akira)
// Status: deprecated | Level: high | ID: 4d11b802-54a7-5aad-bd48-4af510533351

#event_simpleName=*
| (FilePath = *.encrypted OR FilePath = *.locked OR FilePath = *.ransom)
| table([timestamp, ComputerName])
| limit(1000)
